overview: Just when you thought you had a firm grasp on reality, among other things, comes Jim Enright's tale of the blurred line between that which 'is' and that which 'seems to be.' Wicked provides the incredible Jenna Jameson who will demonstrate how very real she is, and a first class cast of the hottest performers in cyberspace. So slip on the glove and have a feel. You may never come back.
tagline: Is it Real...or is it Virtual?
title: Virtual Reality Sixty Nine
